{"tid":691653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"顧客投訴衣服尺碼標示較實際大　英H&M決定更改","createTime":"2018-06-06T03:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T03:12:44.000Z","uid":159163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb125a633881d1a157381c41d781dab1bd80c14c","tid":691653,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/110035_1e7cf0b52e8e3a538ca982d80de70c9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F110035_1e7cf0b52e8e3a538ca982d80de70c9d.png&h=dc318966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國H&amp;M時裝公司收到顧客投訴後，宣布將更改衣服尺碼標示，以符合英國尺碼。<br />\n<br />\n不少顧客曾投訴H&amp;M服裝的實際尺碼比標示的尺碼小，日前更有一名英國女顧客撰寫公開信予H&amp;M公司，指衣服不符實際尺碼會影響她的自我感覺。H&amp;M公司發言人表示，「我們正在採取措施去改變我們的女裝測量方式，以符合英國尺碼」，若以新的測量方式量度，過往標示尺碼12會改為10。<br />\n<br />\n過往，很多顧客投訴H&amp;M的衣服實際尺碼比標示尺碼小太多。今年3月，英國一名顧客帕克（Rebecca Parker）撰寫公開信投訴H&amp;M公司，指自己一向穿12/14碼的衣服，但她卻難以穿上一條標示14碼的H&amp;M牛仔褲。帕克表示，她在H&amp;M購物時，因實際尺碼比所標示的小，而要穿標示更大尺碼的衣服，令她覺得自己很胖，很傷心。<br />\n<br />\n亦有其他英國顧客在twitter發文表達對H&amp;M衣服尺碼的不滿。"},{"pid":"03f9e119716a9b53c3a0b44885848cf4f177501d","tid":691653,"uid":45238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:02:14.000Z","msg":"會唔會因為佢肥咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bc2ea75a68218cf85b42189fb7ddbddacdf6a4","tid":691653,"uid":159163,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/110223_5c0cda3b1e194101a539fef81d68e0a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F110223_5c0cda3b1e194101a539fef81d68e0a0.png&h=878d3b94&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5aa2cce701209e1f6ef37babe06dcb2f430dd4c","tid":691653,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/110252_e00d8afc880066ea895280072cbab952.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F110252_e00d8afc880066ea895280072cbab952.png&h=085c5502&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8984929c392e02674248c0c08a07acba04c105fe","tid":691653,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"so as nike"},{"pid":"b4be7b06d61d81c7bcf49808c0d4f694691fad6b","tid":691653,"uid":159163,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/110352_43fcb41dfc3a67b65c844354ebe94b46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F110352_43fcb41dfc3a67b65c844354ebe94b46.png&h=56785e9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecfcb4882e4a10d5814c3def41ca31053afe5be0","tid":691653,"uid":185683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a041f8b7d245598a55b2ca57d26efec67e32321a","tid":691653,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/06/111243_a8a94f63339cbee282f8571b9e998a9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F06%2F111243_a8a94f63339cbee282f8571b9e998a9c.png&h=b296385e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}